extendedInfo.description: eSubic Tour is a Free Tourist Application, passionately organized by KWT Computer Systems Incorporated. eSubic Tour provides resorts, restaurants, accommodations, traveling and shopping places information located in Subic bay Metropolitan Authority(SBMA). Designed to guide and help tourist be prepared, informed and reach their destinations properly and successfully in SBMA.HOME TAB:Home includes history, population, Climate, geography, and traffic rules inside Subic Bay Metropolitan Authority.Home also includes Gallery of Images of Subic.DIRECTORY TAB:Directory of businesses, institutions and any establishments inside Subic Bay Metropolitan Authority. Including map, general info and image gallery of SBMA.MAP TAB:Online Map of Subic Bay Metropolitan Authority. Internet Connection Required.CREDITS TAB:All you need to know about the application development.
